ttps://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/83750/', '', 'Citalopram, Sertraline, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Duloxetine, Isocarboxazid, Viloxazine, Esketamine, More', 'Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Mometasone, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Beclomethasone dipropionate, Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Flunisolide, Fluticasone, More', 1767369485);
